  "keyFeatures": [
    "Agent engineering platform with LangGraph integration",
    "Composable Runnable interface for chaining components",
    "Universal chat model interface with 20+ provider integrations",
    "Structured tools and function calling support",
    "Prompt templates and prompt engineering utilities",
    "Memory and chat history management",
    "Vector stores and retrieval-augmented generation (RAG)",
    "Document loaders and text splitters",
    "Streaming support for real-time responses",
    "Callbacks and tracing with LangSmith integration",
    "Multi-environment support (Node.js, Browser, Deno, Cloudflare Workers)",
    "Monorepo architecture with modular packages"
